description: Darkness Radio takes a darker turn in the second and third hours of tonight's show.  We talk to a man named "Robert". "Robert" worked at an undisclosed covert Government facility that had to do with Alien activity.  And, the things "Robert" saw, would astound you! This is a must tune-in, must listen episode of Darkness Radio!!
